BOUNTY HUNTER: Relentless pursuer of criminals for profit

The Bounty Hunter pursues criminals and fugitives for profit. Part
detective, part warrior, they combine combat ability with surveillance,
interrogation, and tracking skills that make them relentless pursuers.

Bounty Hunters begin with a strong espionage and investigation skill
set alongside solid weapons training. They choose from Espionage,
Military, Rogue, and Technical categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: PS 9, PE 9.
  Equipment: Body armor, restraints, laser pistol, rifle, tracking
    equipment, and a current bounty list.

